Śledzie  () is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Dźwierzuty, within Szczytno County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  east of Dźwierzuty,  north-east of Szczytno, and  east of the regional capital Olsztyn.
